channel.description:
hell o i want help with pw(portforward).
in pw i want help to twhere i start at it(where to prees on pw)
and i really want to have heklp how to get a [code]Start server[/code] thing.
(im rrelly baad in english so please dont say i dumb!!!)[br][br][size=1]Posted on: September 15, 2008, 07:28:05 am[/size][hr]i do newer get his up!
Open a web browser like internet explorer or Netscape. Enter the ip address of your router in the address bar of your browser. In the picture above the address bar has http://www.google.com in it. Just replace all of that with the ip address of your router. By default the ip address should be set to 192.168.1.1.
